# .gitleaksignore — one FINGERPRINT per line, NOT raw secret values.
# Fingerprint format: <commit-sha>:<file-path>:<rule-id>:<start-line>
#   e.g.  a1b2c3d:config/app.yml:generic-api-key:42
# Get a finding's fingerprint from gitleaks output (the "Fingerprint:" field)
# or `gitleaks detect --report-format json`.
#
# Raw addresses/values do NOT work here (they error as "Invalid entry").
# To allowlist known-safe VALUES globally, add a [allowlist] regex in
# ~/.config/gitleaks.toml instead. The public Base Sepolia testnet wallet
# addresses formerly listed here are now allowlisted there.
